Walking on the streets with music in your ears,you notice a person standing next to his car,it’s obvious that they need help..you hesitate helping them,thinking that you have to be at Codi before 8:45,so that Gaby won’t reduce some of your keys,but you decide to help them cause you are a nice person :)

