1-Fight => it’s impossible to fight cause there is a gun pointed at you => what will you do?
2-Cry => touch the killer feelings =>understand what they want from you (wants your identity => if you have it from previous question,you'll give it to him and you are free to go,arrive to Codi at the right time,tell the story and no one believes you,and Gaby give you minus keys anyway--if you don’t have it,get killed => GAME OVER) 
3-Scream => you start screaming for help,a police officer hears you,they come to help => Free to go! 
